  "texts": [
    "The vehicles added through McLight feature significantly more realistic reflections and strong shadows consistent with the scene.",
    "Vehicle motion.",
    "As shown in Table 5, we compare the motion generation method from user commands with two of our designed baselines: 1.",
    "GPT2Motion, which directly uses LLM to return the motion coordinates; 2.",
    "GPT2Code, which first generates code using LLM and executes it to obtain the vehicle motion."
